    "macroSummary": "US-Iran peace talks have collapsed with Trump announcing a naval blockade of the Strait of Hormuz, triggering classic risk-off flows as oil surges 9% back above $100 and the dollar strengthens sharply. This geopolitical shock is pushing markets toward the stagflation threshold while BTC funding rates turn deeply negative (-0.011) and crypto faces technical breakdown pressure below key levels.",
